Things 3 Plugin
===============

Installation
============
First build the Plugin JAR:
- Clone the repo
- Run ./graldew publishPlugin

Add the plugin to IntelliJ:
- Go to Plugins > Install from disk
- Select the JAR created in the previous step

Usage
=====
- Set the caret to anywhere on the TODO line
- Under the Tools Menu find the Things3
- Click on Add Todo

Your todo item should be added under Inbox list in Things3


